snippet.title: BugsBox VR - Trailer [VR, PlayStation VR]
snippet.description:
Trailer for BugsBox VR, a casual virtual reality game where you need to move your character and push blocks around to defeat the enemy bugs. Developed by PARK ESM, available for PlayStation VR. You can find more information, as well as reviews and ratings here: https://vrgamecritic.com/game/bugsbox-vr
